Localization.Name: Pico the Penguin Luminalia Plushie
Localization.Description: Even Pico the Penguin takes time away from shredding the slopes to celebrate Luminalia. This version of microTech's charming mascot features him in a red and green jacket and holding a Luminalia-themed snowboard.
